summary: This is an FBI administrative document requesting the closure of case 72-MM-113327, which involves Alfredo Rodriguez for obstruction of justice. The document states all investigative and prosecutorial issues have been resolved.

persons.name: Alfredo Rodriguez
persons.context: He is the subject of FBI case 72-MM-113327 for obstruction of justice, which is being recommended for administrative closure.

events.title: Request for Case Closure
events.description: The FBI drafts a request for the administrative closure of case 72-MM-113327 involving Alfredo Rodriguez.

keyFacts: The FBI requested the administrative closure of case number 72-MM-113327.
The case involved Alfredo Rodriguez on a charge of obstruction of justice.
The document states all investigative and prosecutorial issues in the case have been resolved.
The request was drafted and approved within the FBI's Miami field office (Squad PB-2).
